<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">You are wrong and right at the same time. Though this book contains mature themes and you need have a small background of whats happening, this can be<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">You are wrong and right at the same time. Though this book contains mature themes and you need have a small background of whats happening, this can be understood by a middle school or up student. I am in middle school, and though I am very exposed to lots of the material in the book, I understood it fully. It was such a good book. I just want to make sure that your question didn't stop anyone from reading it. It is so good and very educational.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
